; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests null posting with a multi-commodity balance.
; When a transaction has postings in multiple commodities and one null
; posting, the null post must be split into multiple balancing posts.

2024/01/01 Multi-commodity null post
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Expenses:Travel            100 EUR
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-50.00
            -100 EUR  Assets:Cash
              $50.00
             100 EUR  Expenses
              $50.00    Food
             100 EUR    Travel
--------------------
                   0
end test
